DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260720
SUMMARY:[Book] Xiuguluan River Rafting (Sep 30)
DESCRIPTION:Book rafting package on Klook/KKday (gear+shuttle+insurance).\n
 Cost: approx NT$800-1200/person.\nRafting date: Sep 30.\nSearch: klook.com
  "Xiuguluan River Rafting"
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-trip-002@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260726
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260923
SUMMARY:[Book Window] Bus 6739 Sun Moon Lake to Alishan (Sep 24)
DESCRIPTION:Must reserve 2-60 days ahead! Only 1-2 buses/day.\nTravel date:
  Sep 24.\nReserve online or by phone.\nThis is the only direct bus from Su
 n Moon Lake to Alishan.
END:VEVENT

